31st Street, west side, (right, not shown) north of Twenty-first Ave.,
showing in the foreground a rear view of the Peter Rapelje house, which
was demolished in 1925. The buildings at the left are on the west side
of 29th Street. This is a set of four viewed northwestward.
May 1923
Views 2, 3 & 4: March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
